{"id":319101,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-人权律师唐吉田遭羁押，表示将继续坚守/","date":"2013-10-21T15:19:13Z","modified":"2013-10-21T15:19:13Z","title":"维权网 | 人权律师唐吉田遭羁押，表示将继续坚守在维权一线（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div align=\"left\"><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>（维权网信息员向华、孙雨报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span>日下午<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>点<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>分，人权律师刘卫国与张科科在鸡西市拘留所成功会见到唐吉田律师，唐吉田律师自述自己没有任何违法行为，鸡西警方至今未向他送达任何法律文书。唐律师感谢全国律师和公民的鼎力支持与帮助，表示将继续坚守在维权第一线。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日下午，唐吉田律师在陪同杨姓公民就其妻子被长时间非法拘禁向鸡西市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">610</span><span>办公室交涉时，被当场扣押，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日被以“扰乱单位秩序”为由行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>天，关押在鸡西市第二看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>唐吉田律师在行使律师职责时被非法扣押和行政拘留，引起社会各界的极大震惊和强烈抗议。随即，“关注唐吉田团队”发出紧急呼吁书，要求鸡西市政府立即撤销对唐吉田律师行政拘留的处罚，立即还唐吉田律师人身自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日晚，唐吉田律师救援团拟发起“律师权益保障”法律研讨会，全国各地的维权律师及网友纷纷赶往鸡西市，表示对唐吉田律师的关注和声援。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wQK167nLcno/UmURUBo9UZI/AAAAAAAApyc/sB7a-_OY4mg/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE02.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"218\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wQK167nLcno/UmURUBo9UZI/AAAAAAAApyc/sB7a-_OY4mg/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE02.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-L30EDWFTteQ/UmURXo8fqWI/AAAAAAAApy0/mjH9azR2WpM/s1600/%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E7%9C%8B%E5%AE%88%E6%89%80.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"239\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-L30EDWFTteQ/UmURXo8fqWI/AAAAAAAApy0/mjH9azR2WpM/s320/%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E7%9C%8B%E5%AE%88%E6%89%80.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-FvmxUcPU9PM/UmURVsdvL6I/AAAAAAAApyk/d4t5lXcjv3w/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"280\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-FvmxUcPU9PM/UmURVsdvL6I/AAAAAAAApyk/d4t5lXcjv3w/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}